Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.18,0:00:06.24,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}watashi ga umareta asa no machi yuki no naka ni umoreta
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.07,0:00:11.78,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}sore wa sore wa chiisai te de aozora wo aoida
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.09,0:00:18.41,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}sanagara mukashi kara yoku shiru tonari no ano ko no you ni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.14,0:00:23.27,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}katahou no mimitabu de kiku sotsugyou no canon
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.27,0:00:29.23,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}hitori demo daijoubu yo tte mekureteru watashi no story
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.23,0:00:31.51,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}dareka no sei ni shitai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.51,0:00:35.55,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}tsurai naa iya iya
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.55,0:00:41.05,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}kanashikutte naite bakkari itara me ga tokete nakunatta
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.67,0:00:46.47,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}aki ni nari mata fuyu ni nari hitotsu toshi wo totta
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.10,0:00:53.26,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}tooku made nigete iru tsumori demo owaranai kimi no story
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.26,0:00:55.52,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}niya niya waratte iru
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.52,0:00:59.11,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}fugainaiya iya
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.11,0:01:05.25,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}sugari nagara oikakete mitemo ashige ni saretemo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.25,0:01:07.44,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}aita ana wo fusagou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.44,0:01:10.36,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}chigai nai ya iya
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.36,0:01:17.74,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}fugainai ya iya
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.33,0:01:28.36,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}tsurai naa iya iya
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.18,0:00:06.24,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}My hometown lay buried in snow the morning I was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.07,0:00:11.78,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}I looked up at the blue sky with my tiny hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.09,0:00:18.41,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}The face of the girl next door that I've known so well...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.14,0:00:23.27,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}It's as familiar as the graduation canon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.27,0:00:29.23,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Thriving in solitude has been mistaken as my life story.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.23,0:00:31.51,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}I want to blame it on someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.51,0:00:35.55,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}It's so difficult. No, I hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.55,0:00:41.05,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Tears and sorrow caused me to miss my chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.67,0:00:46.47,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Autumn passed, winter came again, and I became a year older.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.10,0:00:53.26,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}You think you've run far away, but your story never ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.26,0:00:55.52,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}And yet, you're smirking.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.52,0:00:59.11,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}It's so cowardly. I hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.11,0:01:05.25,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Even if I have to cling to you, chase after you, and get kicked down...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.25,0:01:07.44,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}...I'll close the hole that's opened...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.44,0:01:10.36,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}...without a doubt. No...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.36,0:01:17.74,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}It's so cowardly. No...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.33,0:01:28.36,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}It's so difficult. I hate it. I hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.02,0:01:35.57,clover,,0,0,0,,Hold that end!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.36,0:01:37.86,clover,,0,0,0,,We don't have enough palettes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.33,0:01:40.28,clover,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't step there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.28,0:01:41.83,clover,,0,0,0,,The mat board still isn't here yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.80,0:01:46.21,clover,,0,0,0,,So, it's the season for the Hamabi Festival again...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.11,0:01:48.40,clover,,0,0,0,,Time sure flies...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.54,0:01:55.01,clover,,0,0,0,,There was another mail from Professor Belshire, inviting her to study abroad.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.18,0:02:00.72,clover,,0,0,0,,Is Hanamoto-san really planning on going back to Nagano after graduation?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.72,0:02:04.18,clover,,0,0,0,,Hanamoto-kun, are you really okay with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.55,0:02:08.95,clover,,0,0,0,,Isn't she just worried that she's getting in your way?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.76,0:02:13.61,clover,,0,0,0,,And that she'll be a bother if she is still in your care after graduation?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.78,0:02:18.02,clover,,0,0,0,,It'll be their last Hamabi Festival...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.47,0:02:20.95,clover,,0,0,0,,Make sure you enjoy every last bit of it, you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.57,0:02:28.05,clover,,0,0,0,,Well, I understand though. Coming from an old guy like me, it doesn't really have much impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.37,0:02:29.71,clover,,0,0,0,,But I'll say it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.81,0:02:31.98,clover,,0,0,0,,Everyone, do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.37,0:02:37.76,clover,,0,0,0,,Huh? Shuu-chan, we're already out of brush cleaners!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.95,0:02:39.90,clover,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.90,0:02:41.84,clover,,0,0,0,,I'll buy some more later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.42,0:02:43.30,clover,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.56,0:02:46.14,clover,,0,0,0,,An old postcard...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.47,0:02:47.71,clover,,0,0,0,,What is this a picture of?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.93,0:02:51.88,clover,,0,0,0,,Oh, that brings back memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.25,0:02:53.86,clover,,0,0,0,,Guess who painted that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.30,0:02:55.25,clover,,0,0,0,,It's by Munch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.64,0:02:56.94,clover,,0,0,0,,Munch...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.07,0:02:59.26,clover,,0,0,0,,You mean the guy who drew this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.26,0:03:01.74,clover,,0,0,0,,That's right. You sure do a good impression, Hagu...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.08,0:03:06.14,clover,,0,0,0,,It's the moonlight reflecting off the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.14,0:03:08.85,clover,,0,0,0,,You figured it out from only that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.85,0:03:10.41,clover,,0,0,0,,I couldn't figure it out at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.40,0:03:14.90,clover,,0,0,0,,This motif appears repeatedly in Munch's paintings.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.46,0:03:18.18,clover,,0,0,0,,It was back when I was in college.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.89,0:03:21.86,clover,,0,0,0,,There was a huge Munch exhibit at the Museum of Modern Art.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.86,0:03:24.48,clover,,0,0,0,,I bought that when I went to see it with some friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.11,0:03:33.51,clover,,0,0,0,,Whoa, this is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.51,0:03:35.19,clover,,0,0,0,,It's the same as that painting we saw earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.84,0:03:37.88,clover,,0,0,0,,Hey, I've been thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.88,0:03:42.99,clover,,0,0,0,,When you stare at it, doesn't the part that's shining look like a path?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.38,0:03:45.69,clover,,0,0,0,,Hey, Harada! Don't fall in!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.79,0:03:50.45,clover,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, maybe this is what the song was talking about in that movie we saw?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.63,0:03:53.26,clover,,0,0,0,,What was that song called?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.92,0:03:55.08,clover,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.50,0:03:56.95,clover,,0,0,0,,It was "Moon River".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.37,0:03:59.43,clover,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.87,0:04:03.17,clover,,0,0,0,,It really feels like I can walk across to the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.42,0:04:06.11,clover,,0,0,0,,No, you can't cross over!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.11,0:04:09.74,clover,,0,0,0,,Or rather, you'd literally end up on "the other side" if you tried crossing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.74,0:04:12.52,clover,,0,0,0,,Hey now, Rika, come over here and stop this idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.02,0:04:15.85,clover,,0,0,0,,If Harada-kun is going, I'm going as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.85,0:04:16.65,clover,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.65,0:04:18.34,clover,,0,0,0,,On second thought, don't come!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.93,0:04:20.78,clover,,0,0,0,,Harada!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.78,0:04:23.20,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm going with Harada-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.16,0:04:27.79,clover,,0,0,0,,Harada! Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.79,0:04:28.70,clover,,0,0,0,,Come back up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.86,0:04:30.92,clover,,0,0,0,,Rika.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.39,0:04:32.22,clover,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.93,0:04:33.82,clover,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.87,0:04:37.17,clover,,0,0,0,,Harada... Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.31,0:04:39.27,clover,,0,0,0,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.41,0:04:41.55,clover,,0,0,0,,Rika!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.56,0:04:44.16,clover,,0,0,0,,Don't, Rika!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.46,0:04:49.05,clover,,0,0,0,,Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.05,0:04:50.18,clover,,0,0,0,,Please don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.49,0:04:51.72,clover,,0,0,0,,Rika!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.19,0:04:57.40,clover,,0,0,0,,Why... After all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.53,0:05:03.65,thoughts,,0,0,0,,We gathered up his remains and somehow managed to organize a small funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.23,0:05:07.41,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Rika wasn't even able to see Harada off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.14,0:05:15.61,thoughts,,0,0,0,,What awaited Rika when she woke up was a lifetime of bodily pain and a tiny package.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.04,0:05:21.56,thoughts,,0,0,0,,In order to escape the pain, she stopped eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.58,0:05:24.23,clover,,0,0,0,,Don't kill yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.59,0:05:26.40,clover,,0,0,0,,You won't be able to go where Harada is!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.75,0:05:29.09,clover,,0,0,0,,You won't be able to see him again in the truest sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.33,0:05:37.26,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Haunted by my words, Rika became unable to chase after Harada.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.70,0:05:40.53,thoughts,,0,0,0,,She tried her hardest to eat, no matter how much came back up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.16,0:05:45.56,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Dragging along her wounded body, she buried herself in the work that Harada left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.91,0:05:49.87,thoughts,,0,0,0,,But I could hear it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.61,0:05:55.34,thoughts,,0,0,0,,There was always a soundless scream coming from her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.67,0:06:00.66,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I was the one who couldn't stand it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.79,0:06:03.14,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I had come to realize...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.05,0:06:10.41,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Although we lived together, it was always myself and them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.43,0:06:15.37,thoughts,,0,0,0,,No matter how much I liked Harada, and no matter how precious Rika was to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.97,0:06:23.69,thoughts,,0,0,0,,...all I could do for the two of them was to watch over their happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.42,0:06:31.07,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Please let them be together, forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.05,0:06:34.35,clover,,0,0,0,,Hanamoto-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.43,0:06:39.54,clover,,0,0,0,,Oh, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.91,0:06:44.24,clover,,0,0,0,,What am I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.59,0:06:47.02,clover,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.02,0:06:47.55,clover,,0,0,0,,What in the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.44,0:06:52.26,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.04,0:06:55.26,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.11,0:06:57.93,clover,,0,0,0,,I've made you try such a thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.29,0:07:01.09,clover,,0,0,0,,We should stay away from each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.07,0:07:04.06,clover,,0,0,0,,We shouldn't be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.26,0:07:08.03,clover,,0,0,0,,I love you, Shuu...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.46,0:07:14.04,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Rika, I wasn't able to send you to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.51,0:07:16.11,thoughts,,0,0,0,,...or support you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.23,0:07:21.73,thoughts,,0,0,0,,But, just like how that girl has allowed me to come this far...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.37,0:07:29.76,thoughts,,0,0,0,,...please let the man who's next to you right now carry you to your future.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.75,0:07:35.85,clover,,0,0,0,,Well then, thank you for taking care of me again this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.28,0:07:40.63,clover,,0,0,0,,I'll come again for the store's opening ceremony, Rika-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.63,0:07:43.40,clover,,0,0,0,,Please visit my place again sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.16,0:07:46.23,clover,,0,0,0,,Pochi is still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.23,0:07:48.61,clover,,0,0,0,,Although he's grown old as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.16,0:07:53.24,clover,,0,0,0,,...I wonder which of us will be the first to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.66,0:07:54.62,clover,,0,0,0,,Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.68,0:07:58.17,clover,,0,0,0,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.71,0:08:05.12,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I almost said, "So you've been there before?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.41,0:08:09.51,thoughts,,0,0,0,,The person who went with her back then is no longer here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.89,0:08:12.96,thoughts,,0,0,0,,He's lost forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.29,0:08:17.08,clover,,0,0,0,,{\an8}A train is arriving on Track 13.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.08,0:08:19.14,clover,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Please wait behind the white line.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.40,0:08:38.70,sign,,0,0,0,,{\fad(276,0)\fay-0.08\fax-0.2\frx2\fry352\frz9.214\move(351,65,336,65,26,2320)}Express Cassiopeia: To Sapporo
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.34,0:08:55.84,clover,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The train on Track 13 is departing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.84,0:08:57.34,clover,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Please watch out for the closing doors.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.37,0:09:04.79,clover,,0,0,0,,Mayama-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.56,0:09:12.99,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Please let the man who's next to you right now carry you to your future.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.40,0:09:18.05,clover,,0,0,0,,{\an8}This is the Cassiopeia, headed for Sapporo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.62,0:09:18.80,clover,,0,0,0,,Mayama-kun, why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.05,0:09:23.50,clover,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The train will stop on the way at Omiya, Utsunomiya, Kooriyama, Fukushima...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.09,0:09:23.50,clover,,0,0,0,,It looks it'll stop at Omiya on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.03,0:09:25.26,clover,,0,0,0,,Let's get off there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.26,0:09:26.75,clover,,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.75,0:09:29.52,clover,,0,0,0,,Would you like to go all the way to Hokkaido?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.39,0:09:32.53,clover,,0,0,0,,You haven't been back in a while, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.53,0:09:35.94,clover,,0,0,0,,I apologize if I misunderstood you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.94,0:09:36.97,clover,,0,0,0,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.21,0:09:39.92,clover,,0,0,0,,It seemed like you wanted to go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.67,0:09:45.77,clover,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.48,0:09:48.38,clover,,0,0,0,,May I inspect your tickets?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.75,0:09:49.73,clover,,0,0,0,,What might your room number be?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.62,0:09:52.92,clover,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry, we...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.92,0:09:56.42,clover,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, is there a room still open?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.12,0:09:58.93,clover,,0,0,0,,Yes, there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.93,0:10:00.96,clover,,0,0,0,,We can still make arrangements for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.96,0:10:01.74,clover,,0,0,0,,Where are you headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.35,0:10:03.56,clover,,0,0,0,,To Sapporo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.17,0:10:11.31,clover,,0,0,0,,It's starting to rain...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.41,0:10:16.68,clover,,0,0,0,,I-It sure is quiet...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.68,0:10:18.63,clover,,0,0,0,,Well, not really, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.38,0:10:21.06,clover,,0,0,0,,H-How should I put it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.86,0:10:24.82,clover,,0,0,0,,We left Ueno at 16:20...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.82,0:10:27.17,clover,,0,0,0,,...so we'll be arriving at Sapporo at nine tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.65,0:10:29.13,clover,,0,0,0,,That's about seventeen hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.49,0:10:33.97,clover,,0,0,0,,That's amazing. It'd only take two hours if we took an airplane.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.67,0:10:39.44,clover,,0,0,0,,I didn't bring my laptop, and all of our files are at the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.44,0:10:41.21,clover,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.54,0:10:45.09,clover,,0,0,0,,We have no choice. Let's just forget about it and relax for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.96,0:10:48.05,clover,,0,0,0,,This is amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.81,0:10:52.20,clover,,0,0,0,,I wonder how long it's been since I last spent so much time doing nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.08,0:10:59.22,clover,,0,0,0,,I see... So everyone pays to buy this kind of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.45,0:11:06.84,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Her monologue slowly melted into the rain-drenched scenery...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.40,0:11:12.90,thoughts,,0,0,0,,It made me feel drowsy, lonely, and somewhat happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.84,0:11:23.54,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I always worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.08,0:11:26.15,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Every time we finished a job...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.45,0:11:28.75,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Every time she sang that song...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.12,0:11:32.79,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Every time she looked up at the distant moon...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.63,0:11:42.80,clover,,0,0,0,,We can't really see anything now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.80,0:11:44.15,clover,,0,0,0,,There's also been so many tunnels.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.63,0:11:47.52,clover,,0,0,0,,Yeah, why don't we get some rest already?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.37,0:11:50.61,clover,,0,0,0,,Mayama-kun, will you be taking a shower?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.61,0:11:53.21,clover,,0,0,0,,Would you mind if I took one first?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.21,0:11:56.57,clover,,0,0,0,,S-Sure. Please go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.95,0:12:02.99,clover,,0,0,0,,U-Um, Rika-san, I'll be fine right here, so please use the room downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.25,0:12:05.15,clover,,0,0,0,,You won't be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.15,0:12:09.13,clover,,0,0,0,,Someone your size won't be able to rest there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.51,0:12:11.63,clover,,0,0,0,,Please sleep in the bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.36,0:12:15.33,clover,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.33,0:12:17.13,sign,,0,0,0,,{\fnCalibri\fs36\c&H8280C3&\pos(358,0)\3c&HE9DCE5&}Mayama's Happiness Savings
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.13,0:12:19.34,sign,,0,0,0,,{\fnCalibri\fs32\pos(358,5)\3c&HE6E6ED&\c&H84A1D1&}Mayama's Happiness Savings
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.13,0:12:19.34,sign,,0,0,0,,{\fnCambria\fs26\pos(633,36)\3c&HE5E1E4&\c&H9B96CA&}Please spend wisely
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.13,0:12:19.34,clover,,0,0,0,,My happiness savings!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.83,0:12:41.92,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.26,0:12:43.52,clover,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.52,0:12:45.16,clover,,0,0,0,,Are you going to sleep like that, Mayama-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.79,0:12:46.95,clover,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.95,0:12:48.89,clover,,0,0,0,,That thing was kinda small.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.50,0:12:55.27,clover,,0,0,0,,I see. I wore mine, since we didn't bring a change of clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.21,0:12:57.25,clover,,0,0,0,,Why don't we sleep then?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.40,0:12:59.25,clover,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.94,0:13:05.43,clover,,0,0,0,,When should I set the alarm for?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.85,0:13:07.83,clover,,0,0,0,,How about around seven?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.83,0:13:08.35,clover,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.15,0:13:10.53,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm turning off the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.85,0:13:11.68,clover,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.89,0:13:18.25,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Asking what time we're waking up...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.06,0:13:20.57,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Setting the alarm clock...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.37,0:13:23.20,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Turning off the light to the room...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.10,0:13:27.71,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Being able to be by her side the entire time she slept...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.31,0:13:31.48,thoughts,,0,0,0,,My heart swelled up so much with happiness...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.54,0:13:33.75,thoughts,,0,0,0,,It was irritating.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.71,0:13:37.11,thoughts,,0,0,0,,My head was pounding.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.21,0:14:11.23,clover,,0,0,0,,Rika-san, does your leg hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.75,0:14:12.88,clover,,0,0,0,,A little.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.41,0:14:15.91,clover,,0,0,0,,I should've brought my cane.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.64,0:14:18.79,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. What about your medicine?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.69,0:14:22.92,clover,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine. I always carry extras.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.46,0:14:26.63,clover,,0,0,0,,Your home is just outside Otaru, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.63,0:14:30.30,clover,,0,0,0,,No, it's actually pretty far from the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.30,0:14:31.52,clover,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.83,0:14:35.78,clover,,0,0,0,,I've seen you watching footage of the city, so I figured you were local.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.37,0:14:39.90,clover,,0,0,0,,Back when I was in high school, I used to come out here often.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.27,0:14:42.98,clover,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'll go rent a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.98,0:14:44.40,clover,,0,0,0,,Is there anything you'd like for me to get?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.15,0:14:48.82,clover,,0,0,0,,Then, please get some milk and biscuits.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.19,0:14:53.80,clover,,0,0,0,,Is this your first time in Hokkaido?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.80,0:14:56.50,clover,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's really vast, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.96,0:14:59.86,clover,,0,0,0,,There aren't very many stoplights or street signs, are there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.23,0:15:05.31,clover,,0,0,0,,We're okay nowadays since we have car navigation, but there isn't anywhere to go for directions if you get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.09,0:15:10.57,clover,,0,0,0,,Mayama-kun, thank you for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.01,0:15:13.10,clover,,0,0,0,,It's made my leg feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.67,0:15:15.76,clover,,0,0,0,,I apologize for the childish pattern...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.28,0:15:19.10,clover,,0,0,0,,...but it was just the right size.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.89,0:15:22.44,clover,,0,0,0,,Mayama-kun, you didn't sleep well, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.44,0:15:24.65,sign,,0,0,0,,{\an7\pos(51,197)\bord1\c&H4D429A&}Super Strong\N{\c&H726154&}Black Mint {\c&H738B5F&}Gum
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.48,0:15:24.35,clover,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.72,0:15:30.82,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm fine. I slept great! Really well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.13,0:15:36.84,thoughts,,0,0,0,,While watching the colorless Sea of Japan to our left...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.30,0:15:43.10,thoughts,,0,0,0,,...we drove endlessly north up the narrow national road surrounded by dark rocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.51,0:15:52.05,thoughts,,0,0,0,,And then, we finally arrived to find the ruins of her home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.52,0:15:59.85,clover,,0,0,0,,Whenever people leave this land, we all do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.89,0:16:08.69,clover,,0,0,0,,An abandoned house will be crushed under the weight of snow and is reduced to ruins by springtime.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.63,0:16:14.24,clover,,0,0,0,,The last time I was here was when my father died.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.40,0:16:19.12,clover,,0,0,0,,Harada-kun stayed behind to oversee the demolition of this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.79,0:16:24.82,clover,,0,0,0,,I was too scared... and couldn't see it through to the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.25,0:16:28.92,clover,,0,0,0,,Don't cry for someone who made you cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.43,0:16:33.00,clover,,0,0,0,,I'll reduce this place to pieces for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.89,0:16:36.04,clover,,0,0,0,,You have me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.49,0:16:39.97,clover,,0,0,0,,You don't need any other places to go home to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.03,0:16:41.74,clover,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.05,0:16:43.02,clover,,0,0,0,,Isn't that so, Rika?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.05,0:17:06.92,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for not coming back for such a long time, Shiro-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.76,0:17:14.47,clover,,0,0,0,,I used to have a dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.53,0:17:17.80,clover,,0,0,0,,He was white and so kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.63,0:17:22.22,clover,,0,0,0,,He was at my house ever since I was a baby...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.54,0:17:26.77,clover,,0,0,0,,...up until I entered high school, so he toughed it out for thirteen years.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.61,0:17:32.19,clover,,0,0,0,,He was always by my side in this empty land.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.38,0:17:34.41,clover,,0,0,0,,Mayama-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.28,0:17:36.20,clover,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.89,0:17:42.12,clover,,0,0,0,,Thank you... for bringing me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.06,0:17:45.96,clover,,0,0,0,,I couldn't have possibly come here on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.73,0:17:50.63,clover,,0,0,0,,But... I was finally able to look upon this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.75,0:17:55.47,clover,,0,0,0,,There really isn't anything left anymore, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.11,0:18:05.52,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I could tell that yet another thing tying her to this world was unraveling.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.72,0:18:13.59,thoughts,,0,0,0,,It was as if the tapes signaling our farewell were being torn off, one by one...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.30,0:18:35.90,clover,,0,0,0,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.55,0:18:43.11,clover,,0,0,0,,Mayama-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.72,0:18:45.72,clover,,0,0,0,,I figured as much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.62,0:18:49.99,clover,,0,0,0,,You'd only allow me to do something like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.99,0:18:51.94,clover,,0,0,0,,...either when you want to hurt yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.94,0:18:55.11,clover,,0,0,0,,...or when you're drawing up some other plan at an incredible pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.53,0:18:56.33,clover,,0,0,0,,Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.33,0:18:57.24,clover,,0,0,0,,What are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.62,0:19:00.70,clover,,0,0,0,,Lying to me about going to Spain together...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.70,0:19:03.61,clover,,0,0,0,,Did you think I would be so easily consoled?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.61,0:19:05.01,clover,,0,0,0,,I wasn't lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.01,0:19:07.12,clover,,0,0,0,,Even though you only ordered one ticket?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.62,0:19:10.11,clover,,0,0,0,,Even though you've looked for a single apartment over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.11,0:19:11.46,clover,,0,0,0,,You looked through my e-mail?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.85,0:19:13.20,clover,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.71,0:19:20.63,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}mizore ni utarete inochi togarasete\NGrinding away my life in the pouring sleet...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.20,0:19:16.04,clover,,0,0,0,,Your e-mail, fax, mail, files, everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.38,0:19:18.72,clover,,0,0,0,,I know everything about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.72,0:19:21.71,clover,,0,0,0,,You're thinking that you don't care about anything, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.63,0:19:27.56,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}susuketa machi de sagashi tsudzuketa\N...I kept searching in that gray town.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.08,0:19:27.11,clover,,0,0,0,,You're thinking about ending everything once you finish all of Harada-san's jobs, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.63,0:19:30.00,clover,,0,0,0,,You made a big mistake in becoming involved with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.24,0:19:35.98,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}kuzuresou na hashi wo iki tomete watari\NAfter holding my breath to cross that rickety bridge...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.00,0:19:31.74,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm following you no matter where you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.13,0:19:33.90,clover,,0,0,0,,Don't you dare think you can die so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.98,0:19:42.89,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}"ki no sei" no saki ni mitsuketa mono wa...\N...what I found beyond my "imagination" was...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.89,0:19:51.47,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}ima kimi dake no tame ni akai hi ni naru\NNow, just for you, I become a red flame...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.28,0:19:45.20,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm begging you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.65,0:19:49.71,clover,,0,0,0,,Please try to live...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.47,0:19:58.04,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}kimi wo atatametai\N...because I want to warm you up...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.15,0:20:06.84,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}kotoba ni sureba buzama na koto mo\N...forever, until my words...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.84,0:20:09.35,clover,,0,0,0,,Ah, damn. This is so uncool.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.84,0:20:18.73,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}uso ja naku naru made zutto\N...can make true all my awkward lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.10,0:20:13.51,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, could you go outside first?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.51,0:20:15.18,clover,,0,0,0,,I-I need to pull myself together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.18,0:20:17.34,clover,,0,0,0,,Please have some tea in the lounge.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.31,0:20:21.90,clover,,0,0,0,,You can't take your bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.43,0:20:34.60,clover,,0,0,0,,I've finished the checkout.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.60,0:20:37.87,clover,,0,0,0,,I've also reserved a flight for 12:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.87,0:20:40.72,clover,,0,0,0,,And um... about earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.20,0:20:41.92,clover,,0,0,0,,Please sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.57,0:20:45.22,clover,,0,0,0,,We still have some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.67,0:20:47.37,clover,,0,0,0,,Let's eat something first.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.98,0:20:51.39,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Two days later...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.05,0:20:55.86,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I headed to Narita to see her off.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.24,0:21:04.39,thoughts,,0,0,0,,After talking about work until the very end, she was sucked into the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.89,0:21:10.32,thoughts,,0,0,0,,When I peeked into her e-mails while cleaning up back at the office...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.03,0:21:13.25,thoughts,,0,0,0,,...I found that the condition for the apartment that she'd been searching for...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.97,0:21:17.38,thoughts,,0,0,0,,...had changed to a two bedroom apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.59,0:21:29.73,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)}arifurete iru kimochi nante sa
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.59,0:21:29.73,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)}It would be so much easier...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.09,0:21:40.19,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}nanimo iwazu ni isso kieteshimaeba
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.09,0:21:40.19,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}...if these stale emotions...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.19,0:21:43.61,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,raku ni nareru no ni
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.19,0:21:43.61,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,...could just disappear without a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.61,0:21:52.74,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}sorezore no michi wo yuku sono wakaremichi
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.61,0:21:52.74,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}At the crossroads where we split ways...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.29,0:22:06.22,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}mou nidoto au koto no nai deai wa kanashisugiru
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.29,0:22:06.22,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}...it saddens me to think we may never meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.22,0:22:08.96,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,tarinai kimochi wo mochiyotte
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.22,0:22:08.96,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,Despite adding the emotions that are lacking...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.96,0:22:11.82,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,atatameta saki kara hieteitte
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.96,0:22:11.82,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,...things cool off just as soon as I warm them...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.82,0:22:16.16,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}sonna hazu naitte shinjiteru
